One of the most important things I did to remove tan ✨

1️⃣ Cleansing – Twice a day with an AHA-based cleanser to gently exfoliate and wash away dirt, oil, and impurities.
2️⃣ Sunscreen – I swear by the Plix sunscreen – it’s super lightweight, leaves zero white cast, and gives SPF 50 protection! Bonus? It protects, repairs and prevents 🌞
3️⃣ Eat clean – Your skin reflects what you eat. Hydrate and fuel up with the right foods 🥗💧

Little changes, big difference 💫
